# Archon writes per-run research/scratch here (brain-dump-* dirs, etc.). A
# committed scratch file caused a cross-PR merge collision (2026-06-18).
# Ignoring the dir stops NEW scratch from being tracked; already-committed
# reference docs stay tracked. Sanitizer sources from git ls-files.
